                            "termSource": null,
                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "<p>The entire <em>Hemerocallis citrina</em> cv. \u2018Datonghuanghua\u2019 plant was collected from Yuzhou district of Datong city, Shanxi province, China in August, 2022. Roots, stems, leaves and flowers from H. citrina were separated and conveyed to BioMarker Technologies Co. (Beijing, China) with drikold.</p>",
                        "uri": "",
                        "version": "",
                        "parameters": [
                            {
                                "comments": [],
