                    },
                    {
                        "comments": [],
                        "name": "Chromatography",
                        "protocolType": {
                            "comments": [],
                            "annotationValue": "Chromatography",
                            "termSource": null,
                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "<p>The analytical conditions were as follows: chromatographic instrument: SCIEX ExionLC AC; chromatographic column: Agilent SB-C18 1.8 \u03bcm, 2.1 mm x 100 mm; mobile phase A: 0.1% formic acid aqueous solution; mobile phase B: 0.1% formic acid acetonitrile; elution gradient, the proportion of phase B is 5% in 0.0 min; the proportion of phase B increases linearly to 95% in 9.0 min, and maintains at 95% for 1 min; 10.0-11.1 min, the proportion of phase B decreases to 5%, and equilibrates at 5% to 14.0 min; flow rate, 0.35 mL/min; column temperature 40 \u00b0C; injection volume 4 \u03bcL.</p>",
